{"members":[{"header_text":" وَ عَنْ  قَتَادَةَ : ","body_text":"فِي قَوْلِهِ: <quranic_text>«سَبْعَ سَمٰاوٰاتٍ وَ مِنَ الْاَرْضِ مِثْلَهُنَّ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الطلاق۱۲]</footnote> قَالَ فِي كُلِّ سَمَاءٍ وَ كُلِّ اَرْضٍ خَلْقٌ مِنْ خَلْقِهِ وَ اَمْرٌ مِنْ اَمْرِهِ وَ قَضَاءٌ مِنْ قَضَائِهِ.","translation":"","aligned_body":"فِي قَوْلِهِ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text سَبْعَ سَمٰاوٰاتٍ وَ مِنَ الْاَرْضِ مِثْلَهُنَّ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الطلاق ۱۲ TAG_CLOSE:footnote قَالَ فِي كُلِّ سَمَاءٍ وَ كُلِّ اَرْضٍ خَلْقٌ مِنْ خَلْقِهِ وَ اَمْرٌ مِنْ اَمْرِهِ وَ قَضَاءٌ مِنْ قَضَائِهِ"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلِهِ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"سبع","display":"سَبْعَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"سماوات","display":"سَمٰاوٰاتٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الارض","display":"الْاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"مثلهن","display":"مِثْلَهُنَّ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الطلاق","display":"الطلاق"},{"kind":"word","token":"۱۲","display":"۱۲"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"كل","display":"كُلِّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"سماء","display":"سَمَاءٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"كل","display":"كُلِّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ارض","display":"اَرْضٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"خلق","display":"خَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"خلقه","display":"خَلْقِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"امر","display":"اَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"امره","display":"اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","d